## Project

**Afilo Digital Marketplace** - A cutting-edge headless e-commerce platform specializing in digital software products

- **Repository**: [afilo-nextjs-shopify-app](https://github.com/code-craka/afilo-nextjs-shopify-app)
- **Live Demo**: [app.afilo.io](https://app.afilo.io)
- **Customer Portal**: [account.afilo.io](https://account.afilo.io)

Built with ❤️ using Next.js 15, TypeScript, and Shopify Storefront API